<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1 class="hero-title">
        惰性に負けず、<br />
        毎日ノートが書ける
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">
        Notlyは、習慣化に特化したシンプルで高速なデスクトップノートアプリです。<br />
        あなたの思考を妨げない、究極のプライベート空間。
      </p>
      <div class="hero-cta">
        <a href="/download" class="btn btn-primary">ダウンロード (Windows)</a>
        <a href="#features" class="btn btn-secondary">機能を見る</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-image">
      <div class="image-wrapper">
        <img src="/images/screenshot_light.png" alt="Notly App Interface" class="screenshot-light" height="600" width="600" />
        <img src="/images/screenshot_dark.png" alt="Notly App Interface" class="screenshot-dark" height="600" width="600" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding: 8rem 0 4rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  /* Removed background glow */

  .hero-content {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
    color: var(--text-color);
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .hero-image {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .image-wrapper {
    /* Removed 3D transform and rotation */
    max-width: 900px;
    width: 100%;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    background: var(--bg-color);
    position: relative;
  }
  
  .image-wrapper img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    opacity: 0.9; /* Slightly muted image to blend better */
  }

  /* Show light screenshot in light mode, dark screenshot in dark mode */
  .screenshot-light {
    display: block;
    position: relative;
  }

  .screenshot-dark {
    display: none;
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .screenshot-light {
    display: none;
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
  }

  :global([data-theme="dark"]) .screenshot-dark {
    display: block;
    position: relative;
  }

  /* Fallback for system preference */
  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    :global(:root:not([data-theme="light"])) .screenshot-light {
      display: none;
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
    }
    :global(:root:not([data-theme="light"])) .screenshot-dark {
      display: block;
      position: relative;
    }
  }

  /* Removed glow element */
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero-title {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>
